TextEng: Don't worry, I won't hurt you.
Who are you old man? What are you doing here?
You not worry. Me not hurt you.
Text: 너 걱정 마. 나 너 안 다치게 해.

TextEng: I need to ask you some questions.
Who you be, old man? Why you here?
Text: 너 누구야, 할아버지? 왜 여기 있어?

TextEng: Me need ask you stuff.
How have you avoided capture by the Luskan army?
Text: 러스칸 군한테 어떻게 잡히지 않고 피하셨어요?

TextEng: Goodbye.
How did a blind man help the children leave the city?
Text: 맹인이 어떻게 아이들을 도시 밖으로 내보내셨어요?

TextEng: How a blind man help kiddies leave city?
Text: 눈먼 사람이 어떻게 아이들 도시 나가게 도와줬어?

TextEng: How come Luskan not catch you yet?
Follow me, old man. I'll take you to safety.
You follow me, old man. Me take you somewhere safe.
Text: 너 나 따라와, 할아버지. 나 너 안전한 데 데려다줄게.

TextEng: What are you talking about?
What you mean?
Never heard of you.
Back door? This place doesn't have a back door.
Back door? This place no got back door!
Where can I find this back door?
Text: 그 뒷문을 어디서 찾을 수 있어요?

TextEng: Where me find secret back door?
Thanks for the info! I'm going to use it to find Aribeth and Maugrim!
Text: 정보 감사합니다! 아리베스와 모그림을 찾는 데 쓸게요!

TextEng: Me going to use door for finding Maugrim and Aribeth.
Text: 나 그 문 모그림이랑 아리베스 찾는 데 쓸 거야.
